data.description:
Virtual showings available upon request, just ask. New kitchen equipment,  new pool equipment,  roof 2011, washer/dryer 2020, roof fully inspected, central vacuum, property double fenced,  hurricane proof windows and a lot more!
Are you ready to dive into the ultimate oasis of comfort and luxury? Well, get your swim trunks and sunscreen ready because this magnificent 2-story house with a pool and spa is about to make a splash on the market in Boynton Beach, FL! Say hello to your dream home in the sought-after Lyons Ranches community, where low HOA fees and a pet-friendly atmosphere make life a breeze.
This spacious abode boasts 4 bedrooms plus a loft, offering ample room for all your needs and desires. Need a little extra privacy for your guests or in-laws? No problem! The first floor features a convenient bedroom with a full bathroom, ensuring your loved ones feel right at home. With a total of 3 full bathrooms, you can say goodbye to those morning traffic jams outside the washroom door!
Prepare to be wowed as you step into the grand living room, where memories are waiting to be made. Whether you're hosting a movie night with friends or a formal dinner party, the huge open living room and dining room provide the perfect backdrop for all your entertaining needs. But wait, there's more! Step outside onto the screened patio and let the gentle breeze whisk your worries away. Enjoy your morning coffee or sip on a sunset cocktail while taking in the breathtaking views of the corner 0.3 acre lot adjacent to the pristine preserve.
Calling all car enthusiasts! This property features not only a 2-car garage but also enough space for an additional 6 cars! That's right, you'll never have to worry about parking again. Your car collection will finally have a place to call home.

With over 2400 square feet of living space and a total of over 3400 square feet, this residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. The possibilities are endless when it comes to creating your own personal haven within these walls. Let your imagination run wild and turn this house into your dream home.
And the perks don't stop there. Commuting has never been easier with the Florida Turnpike just a stone's throw away. Say goodbye to those long, tiresome drives and hello to a stress-free journey to work or play.

So, whether you're a water enthusiast, a car aficionado, or simply seeking a place to call home, this 4-bedroom gem in Boynton Beach is ready to fulfill your every desire. Don't miss out on the opportunity of a lifetime - dive headfirst into luxury living at its finest.
